title: Quinn q skill bug (I think)
body:
When I've played against Quinn now several games as renekton whenever I'm blinded my w doesn't stun her at all like if the skill misses. I'm not 100% sure, but I think it doesn't do damage either whenever I use W as renekton when she has used the Q skill. 

Is it supposed to be like that or is it just a bug?

replies.body: das isn bug. hab den auch schin mit xin gemeldet... nix passiert
Wir sind hier im deutschen Forum, da kannst du auch ruhig deutsch schreiben.
